What type of information does this site provide? Why?
It provides information on JPEGs and what they are, how they look in hexdump, etc.

How would digital forensics expert use this information?
Since JPEGs are a common image file type, you can use this information to find JPEGs that have been deleted by criminals
______________________________________________________________________________________
What is it for?
To give you a guide to finding different file types in hexdump

What information do you need to recover:
an Excel document?
D0 CF 11 E0 is the start

a Word document?
D0 CF 11 E0 is the start

a ZIP file? 
50 4B 03 04 is the start and PK is the header
